{"tid":514001,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人諗過Tom and Jerry入面，Jerry都係仆街仔","createTime":"2017-12-30T06:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T16:27:34.000Z","uid":143499,"like":237,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"75ddc93d8b96fc675121b930d070d97ae11530ad","tid":514001,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:29:54.000Z","msg":"有一半以上嘅集數都係Tom想捉Jerry交差或者撚化Jerry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係其餘嘅集數根本上係Jerry撩人者賤， 偷完嘢食仲要特登搞鳩Tom<br />\n<br />\n仲要識借刀搵隻狗或者Tom個主人收拾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事實證明兩個都咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過問番同齡啲friend，個個都話Jerry係好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393ef9d6f11b3a1f7ebd048d030b2f2fca351f76","tid":514001,"uid":119456,"like":108,"dislike":0,"score":108,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:38:18.000Z","msg":"因為你d同齡朋友都係仆街仔"},{"pid":"44982b858f0c17b92d073838d466601526b10d4c","tid":514001,"uid":2566,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:40:20.000Z","msg":"一早好憎隻老鼠"},{"pid":"6deb5c5fc4cb2f6d5cb33e96cab28546fd4c0fbf","tid":514001,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"393ef9d6f11b3a1f7ebd048d030b2f2fca351f76","tid":514001,"uid":119456,"like":108,"dislike":0,"score":108,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:38:18.000Z","msg":"因為你d同齡朋友都係仆街仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:41:22.000Z","msg":"我啲生活圈子有邊個唔係仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算毒撚嚟講我都係仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8c8c0042b8f2182711d7454e64c4a4a1fe90ea","tid":514001,"uid":148511,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:55:45.000Z","msg":"細個睇覺得tom係仆街仔<br />\n大個發現jerry先至係真正仆街果個"},{"pid":"96f4970faefca80532e4eb07784a4a3fd2703dee","tid":514001,"uid":5455,"like":142,"disli