\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f785d60711ba1ab51f3217ea19a58836fc323a","tid":514001,"uid":13802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:27:06.000Z","msg":"jerry 正一死仆街來<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176034f90b2a65ceea033d31d6cf2a3874fd6453","tid":514001,"uid":90457,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:36:10.000Z","msg":"每逢Tom發現玩大咗都會驚Jerry出事仲會諗辦法補救，但係Jerry成日濫用Tom嘅悔疚感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843f1f67722c823d850a1890e7c39d71754c6ec9","tid":514001,"uid":90457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:40:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個睇得好開心<br />\n不過諗返套野應該唔係畀細路睇.玩槍玩炸彈食煙&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n分年代，舊嗰批會多啲暴力嘢而且冇乜對白，有集係紅番做主題，啲豆丁攞斧頭割Tom個頭皮<br />\n越新反而越兒童向"}]}